OL,3,CBurglar who 'targeted elderly' and
OL,4,Cstole jewellery and war medals jailed
OL,6,FA burglar who "mainly targeted
OL,7,Fvulnerable and elderly people's
OL,8,Fproperties during the daytime" was
OL,9,Fcaught after his DNA was found on a
OL,10,Fgardening glove.
OL,12,FMacorley Collins, 27, has been jailed
OL,13,Ffor 32 months after he stole war
OL,14,Fmedals, jewellery and other expensive
OL,15,Fitems from homes in Stockport.
OL,17,FCollins, of Appleby Close in Adswood,
OL,18,FStockport, pleaded guilty to 10
OL,19,Foffences he committed between
OL,20,FSeptember and December last year, at
OL,21,FManchester Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
