OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1772227258
OL,3,CBurglar who 'targeted elderly' and
OL,4,Cstole jewellery and war medals jailed
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,7,Fhe first targeted an elderly woman's
OL,8,Fhome while she was on a walk, stealing
OL,9,Fjewellery worth around #3,000 as well
OL,10,Fas medication she relied on.
OL,12,FIn further burglaries, GMP said
OL,13,FCollins took a Playstation 5, a Rolex
OL,14,Fwatch, a Platinum ring, two golden
OL,15,Fwatches and a mountain bike worth
OL,16,F#3,800.
OL,18,FA GMP spokesperson said: "In one of
OL,19,Fhis last burglaries, Collins took
OL,20,Fseveral First World War medals and a
OL,21,Fmilitary OBE.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1772227258
OL,3,CBurglar who 'targeted elderly' and
OL,4,Cstole jewellery and war medals jailed
OL,6,F"During one of the December
OL,7,Fburglaries, a gardening-style glove
OL,8,Fwas located in the middle of the
OL,9,Fgarden and after being forensically
OL,10,Fseized and examined, DNA was obtained
OL,11,Fwhich produced a match to Collins. He
OL,12,Fwas subsequently arrested and
OL,13,Finvestigative work mapped him to
OL,14,Fseveral of the locations at the time
OL,15,Fof the burglaries.
OL,17,F"He was later charged with four of
OL,18,Fthem, with a further six taken into
OL,19,Fconsideration at sentencing, after
OL,20,FCollins admitted to them."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1772227258
OL,3,CBurglar who 'targeted elderly' and
OL,4,Cstole jewellery and war medals jailed
OL,6,FPC Lucy Ward, from GMP's Stockport
OL,7,Fdistrict, said: "Collins committed
OL,8,Fmultiple burglaries in the Stockport
OL,9,Farea, helping himself to everything
OL,10,Ffrom expensive jewellery to family
OL,11,Fheirlooms. His brazen tactics of
OL,12,Foperating during the daytime show a
OL,13,Fclear disregard for people and their
OL,14,Fproperty.
OL,16,F"Following a thorough investigation,
OL,17,Finvolving the DNA retrieval of a glove
OL,18,Fleft at the scene by Collins, he
OL,19,Fadmitted guilt and was charged with
OL,20,Fburglary offences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
