CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1772227258
OL,3,CBurglar who 'targeted elderly' and
OL,4,Cstole jewellery and war medals jailed
OL,6,F"People should be able to feel safe
OL,7,Fwithin their own homes, and we will
OL,8,Falways investigate burglaries when
OL,9,Fthey come into us. If you have any
OL,10,Finformation or concerns about
OL,11,Fburglaries in your area, please do get
OL,12,Fin touch with us."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
